<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:26:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>总理的律师告诉法庭，内塔尼亚胡只能在 2025 年 3 月的腐败审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/pms-lawyers-tell-court-netanyahu-can-only-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-march-2025/00000190-5605-def3-a5b6-de2755a00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的律师表示，他们需要九个月的时间才能提出辩方的陈述。耶路撒冷地方法院的审判因调查内容、新冠肺炎和战争导致法院关闭等争论而多次停止</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:18:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/pms-lawyers-tell-court-netanyahu-can-only-testify-in-corruption-trial-in-march-2025/00000190-5605-def3-a5b6-de2755a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡助手担心利库德集团最高议员将破坏正统派豁免法案草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-aides-fear-top-likud-lawmaker-will-sabotage-haredi-draft-exemption-bill/00000190-557c-dc65-abff-7d7f83860000</link><description>讨论该法案的委员会主席、利库德集团议员尤利·埃德尔斯坦(Yuli Edelstein)表示，“如果该法案不能以广泛共识获得通过，它就根本不会通过。”在反对派议员反对后，埃德尔斯坦还推迟了议会关于延长以色列国防军预备役服役的投票</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-aides-fear-top-likud-lawmaker-will-sabotage-haredi-draft-exemption-bill/00000190-557c-dc65-abff-7d7f83860000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员：与以色列合作解决武器延误问题，重型炸弹转移仍停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-working-with-israel-to-resolve-arms-delay-heavy-bomb-transfer-still-halted/00000190-55b2-dc65-abff-7dbbff410000</link><description>华盛顿的国防部长约夫·加兰特描述了军备“瓶颈”方面的“重大进展”。他还批评内塔尼亚胡公开哀叹总理所谓的“故意”延迟武器运输</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-working-with-israel-to-resolve-arms-delay-heavy-bomb-transfer-still-halted/00000190-55b2-dc65-abff-7dbbff410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会提出法案，永久禁止半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-parliament-advances-bill-to-make-law-banning-al-jazeera-permanent/00000190-54c0-dac0-a798-77d789710000</link><description>该法案永久立法目前是一项暂停外国媒体广播的临时命令，如果被认为损害国家安全，将返回政府委员会进一步审议</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 18:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-parliament-advances-bill-to-make-law-banning-al-jazeera-permanent/00000190-54c0-dac0-a798-77d789710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡最后一次国会演讲猛烈抨击民主党。这个有不同的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-last-congress-speech-slammed-democrats-this-one-has-a-different-target/00000190-556a-de50-af9b-7fee35df0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡最近在2011年和2015年的国会演讲的目标是削弱巴拉克·奥巴马总统及其民主党。这次剧本反转了</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 18:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-26/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-last-congress-speech-slammed-democrats-this-one-has-a-different-target/00000190-556a-de50-af9b-7fee35df0000</guid></item><item><title>鲍曼惨败后，美国进步人士能否在不疏远选民的情况下应对亲以色列机器？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</link><description>众议员贾马尔·鲍曼的盟友表示，他周二的失败不应被视为对美国人对加沙战争看法的公投，而他的批评者则表示，这表明对以色列持批评态度是一种选举责任。哪个更准确？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/can-progressives-tackle-the-pro-israel-machine-after-bowmans-crushing-defeat/00000190-5530-dc65-abff-7d3b59640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 264 天：联合国表示加沙援助人员面临的风险“无法忍受”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，由于内塔尼亚胡政府提出的要求减少，美国对以色列的武器运输已放缓 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特表示，即使美国和以色列存在分歧，“我们也会闭门解决” ■ 以色列监狱管理局一直在隐瞒信息消息人士称，自战争开始以来，巴勒斯坦囚犯获得的食物数量如下： 战争进入 264 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-264-un-says-risk-to-aid-workers-in-gaza-intolerable/00000190-555b-de50-af9b-7fffdece0000</guid></item><item><title>我的高中毕业生面临着以色列有史以来最黯淡的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</link><description>我可以诚实地向我的学生保证国家和以色列国防军会保护他们吗？或者以色列仍将是一个民主国家？不会发生内战吗？他们在这里将过着怎样的生活？</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-high-school-graduates-are-facing-the-bleakest-future-israel-has-ever-known/00000190-5406-dc65-abff-7c2fb42c0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列减少了巴勒斯坦安全囚犯的食物，并隐瞒了数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</link><description>自10月7日起，监狱内食物大幅减少，囚犯体重减轻，甚至挨饿。当以色列最高法院听取有关此事的请愿书时，极右翼部长本格维尔表示这是一项“威慑措施”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-reduces-food-for-palestinian-security-prisoners-conceals-data-sources-say/00000190-542e-de5e-abd0-ff7ee9580000</guid></item><item><title>事实还是虚构：以色列受到全球谴责是否不公平？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</link><description>“有偏见、预定、虚伪”：以色列的支持者这样形容国际社会在人权和国际法方面的态度。事实上，在加沙战争之前，令人震惊的是以色列所享受的长期、免费的​​旅程</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/fact-or-fiction-is-israel-unfairly-singled-out-for-global-condemnation/00000190-5053-d37f-a392-7afbfbaf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列知名人士在《纽约时报》撰文敦促国会废除内塔尼亚胡的演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</link><description>该报告由包括前总理巴拉克和前摩萨德负责人在内的六名以色列人共同撰写，皮尔斯敦促国会撤回内塔尼亚胡的邀请，“因为大部分以色列人对内塔尼亚胡先生的政府失去了信心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israelis-pen-op-ed-in-new-york-times-urging-congress-to-axe-pm-speech/00000190-5471-de50-af9b-7ffdfb730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长赞扬法国极右党主席，打破以色列官方抵制全国集会的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</link><description>侨民部长阿米凯·奇克利赞扬了法国极右翼全国集会主席乔丹·巴尔德拉的演讲，他在演讲中宣布两国解决方案“过时”，巴勒斯坦建国是“恐怖的奖励”。奇克利办公室：“我们与勒庞党有良好的接触”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太人，滚出这座城市！”：犹太儿童在伦敦涉嫌仇恨犯罪中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</link><description>一群东正教男孩在中央地铁站遭到当地另一所学校的孩子们的袭击。其中一名男孩的母亲说：“他们把他的头撞到墙上，一颗牙齿脱落了。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩的战争不会是与真主党的决斗；以色列将面临伊朗的整个抵抗轴心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</guid></item><item><title>摇摇欲坠的内塔尼亚胡联盟改变了正统派的现状——变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡对最高法院对草案裁决的回应具有误导性和煽动性。一些人预计他会继续宣传甘茨的“豁免法”，只是为了争取时间，因为他知道法院会否决它</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</guid></item><item><title>两名士兵在加沙非装甲坦克爆炸中丧生后，以色列军队收紧了协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</link><description>&amp;#39;那是一个错误。消息人士称，这付出了沉重的代价，因为在调查士兵死亡事件时，以色列陆军指令下令在南部前线的每辆坦克上安装铭牌</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员相信，只有在以色列国防军离开拉法之后，美国才会向以色列施压以达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦官员表示，哈马斯领导人确信美国不会努力达成停火，而是会拖延直到加沙的激烈战斗结束。他说，以色列军队离开拉法可能是“在各方，特别是美国人放弃之前重新启动谈判的最后机会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院即使没有组建新政府，也可能为新的正统派犹太人铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</link><description>高等法院强制征召犹太学生的裁决不会让内塔尼亚胡的联盟垮台，因为他和他的极端正统派伙伴只是想避免不可避免的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列负担沉重的公众感到沮丧。它不会让军方通过象征性的正统征兵而逃脱惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</link><description>加沙正在进行的战争凸显了以色列国防军服役人员与国家豁免人员之间的不平等有多么严重。法院的裁决为新的服役模式和替代的国民服役形式创造了机会。如果参谋长联手回避这个问题，一波愤怒可能会危及“人民军队”模式</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</guid></item><item><title>勇敢：以色列可以让黎巴嫩回到石器时代，但不希望与真主党发生战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</link><description>报道：以色列对叙利亚和黎巴嫩发动空袭；据说有两人在大马士革附近丧生 ■ 美国高级官员：与以色列合作解决武器延误问题，重型炸弹转移仍然停止 ■ 德国“紧急”要求公民离开黎巴嫩 ■ 内塔尼亚胡回击加兰特呼吁私下解决美以争端 ■ 报告：随着以色列袭击加沙北部和中部营地，以色列国防军和哈马斯在拉法的战斗加剧 ■ 从黎巴嫩向梅图拉发射的反坦克导弹，房屋遭到破坏；火箭弹落在该市后，两座建筑物起火；阿维维姆的房屋遭到反坦克导弹袭击 ■《华尔街日报》：官员称，由于以色列提出的新要求减少，美国武器运输放缓</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</guid></item></channel></rss>